Status: Name: Package name.  Where a package is in CVS, this is its `component' name
Status: S=supported, U=unsupported, X=to be reassigned, J=supported by JAC
CVS status: yes=in CVS; obsolete=in the obsolete tree; thirdparty=in the thirdparty tree; java=this is a java package name, rather than a component name
Maintainer: A contact name.  Components which are in CVS should have a <role>owner</role> element in their component.xml, indicting the owner/maintainer
Copyright: the copyright owner.  Where this is CLRC, the licence will be GPL
